  tools/thiênbăng <command> [args]

Living Extension:
  presence      Show thiênbăng presence
  pulse         Runtime heartbeat + evidence
  immune        Boundary leak scan
  breathe       restart + gate + pulse
  reflect       Show layer reflection
  dictionary    Print src/thienbang.si if present
  gate          Delegate runtime gate to tools/thiên
  status        Delegate status to tools/thiên

